   Scholarships and Fellowships (IRS Publication 520)
   http://www.irs.ustreas.gov/prod/forms_pubs/pubs/p520toc.htm
   This IRS publication covers the rules for scholarships, fellowships,
   and tuition reductions and tax rules for those studying abroad under
   scholarships or fellowships.
   Related Topics: Graduate/professional  Study outside the U.S.
   Scholarships and grants  Fellowships  Taxes
   __________________________________________________________________


                                 Three Stars
                               # Ratings:  210
                               # Visits:  3711

   Fulbright Program (US State Dept)
   http://exchanges.state.gov/education/fulbright/
   The Fulbright Program provides grants for graduate students, scholars
   and professionals from the US and other countries. It is designed to
   "increase mutual understanding between the people of the US and the
   people of other countries..."
   Related Topics: Graduate/professional  International students  Study
   outside the U.S.  Scholarships and grants
   __________________________________________________________________


                                 Three Stars
                               # Ratings:  137
                               # Visits:  1710

   US Network for Education Information (US Dept of Education)
   http://www.ed.gov/NLE/USNEI/
   USNEI presents basic information about education in the United States
   that is of interest to students who wish to study in the US; and
   extensive links to sources of information to assist U.S. students who
   wish to study abroad.
   Related Topics: International students  Study outside the U.S.
   Work/study outside the U.S.
   __________________________________________________________________


                                 Three Stars
                               # Ratings:  30
                               # Visits:  513

   Travel Warnings and Consular Information Sheets, US State Dept.
   http://travel.state.gov/travel_warnings.html
   Before you head to your destination, please check this site compiled by
   the U.S. State Department. The site offers consular information sheets,
   travel warnings, and public announcements.
   Related Topics: Study outside the U.S.  Travel alerts  Services and
   info  Work/study outside the U.S.
   __________________________________________________________________


